Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你可可  是熱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真會添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是全套的國王待遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了千秋  借套衣服給我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼態度啊  求人的方法就這麼一種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最會裝撒嬌的小女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  衣服還要等上一段時間才會乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就交給我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來糾正冬馬的小女兒脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  藤岡什麼時候來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  藤岡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  快把衣服借我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這樣下去  有點兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋衣服借來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是故意找麻煩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來夏樹昨天這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩把刷子嘛  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  看我這招  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  把那個類似手柄的東西給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬馬  再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招  看招  看招…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  男子漢的恩仇都要雙倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身為男子漢  我要從你那兒把衣服奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？只因為你是女生  沒衣服穿感到很為難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬馬   我的衣服借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  你就借衣服給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  不  借
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊  突然下起雨來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快借給我  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不借就不借
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  千秋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借衣服給我吧  我知錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好孩子  還是會求人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我房間來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好求你就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別當沒事兒人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要注意態度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香都歡迎你了  你這什麼態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了  藤岡也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脫了快脫了  總之先泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是何事啊？
