Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這糖真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟寶石一樣  紅豔豔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些天然色素是提取蟲子的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點兒  內田
